\s1 Jonah Prays
\p The \nd Lord\nd* sent \w a|strong="H3068"\w* huge fish to swallow Jonah, and Jonah was in the stomach of the fish three days and three nights.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 \w Jonah|strong="H3124"\w* prayed \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \nd \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w*\nd* \w his|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w from|strong="H3117"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w stomach|strong="H4578"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w fish|strong="H1709"\w*
